<section class="features">
	<div class="features-container">
		<h2 class="features-title">Why This Pilot?</h2>
		<p class="features-subtitle">
			The Riga Temporary Use Competence Center addresses three key objectives aligned with the city's sustainable development strategy.
		</p>
		<div class="features-grid">
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#008080" stroke-width="2"/>
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6" stroke="#008080" stroke-width="2"/>
						<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2" fill="#008080"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="feature-title">Reduce Vacancy</h3>
				<p class="feature-description">
					Activate underused buildings and land in Riga's city center, transforming empty spaces into community assets.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#008080" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="feature-title">Support Local Needs</h3>
				<p class="feature-description">
					Create opportunities for community initiatives, cultural activities, and social enterprises to thrive.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-card">
				<div class="feature-icon">
					<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path d="M12 3v18M12 3l-3 3M12 3l3 3M9 6H7a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2M15 6h2a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-2" stroke="#008080" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
						<circle cx="7" cy="13" r="2" fill="#008080"/>
						<circle cx="17" cy="13" r="2" fill="#008080"/>
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="feature-title">Governance Lab</h3>
				<p class="feature-description">
					Develop and refine contracts, policies, and frameworks for scalable temporary use across the city.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.features {
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		background: #fafafa;
	}

	.features-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.features-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #333;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.features-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: #666;
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 3rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.feature-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		width: 64px;
		height: 64px;
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.feature-icon svg {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.feature-title {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #333;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.feature-description {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #666;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 968px) {
		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.feature-card {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.features {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.features-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.features-subtitle {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
